		{"id":"22ab3c16a46ecaee","type":"text","text":"```ebnf\nrpc_decl = `rpc_service` ident `{`\n    rpc_method+\n`}`\n```","x":4180,"y":2500,"width":580,"height":120},
		{"id":"fe11438157ac6987","type":"text","text":"```ebnf\nmetadata = `(` commasep(ident[`:` single_value]) `)`\n```","x":4100,"y":1620,"width":580,"height":80,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"44f59d5165710b84","type":"text","text":"**Notes**\n- Make use of -re-defined attributes","x":4100,"y":1720,"width":580,"height":100},
		{"id":"cea0cb0f37bbd295","type":"text","text":"- [ ] compiler Known Attributes\n    - [ ] [[project/tests/TESTING#`id n` (on a table field)|`id:n`]]\n    - [ ] [[project/tests/TESTING#`deprecated` (on a field)|deprecated]]\n    - [ ] [[project/tests/TESTING#`required` (on a non-scalar table field)|required]]\n    - [ ] [[project/tests/TESTING#`bit_flags` (on an unsigned enum)|bit_flags]]\n    - [ ] [[project/tests/TESTING#`nested_flatbuffer \"table_name\"` (on a field)|`nested_flatbuffer:\"table_name\"`]]\n    - [ ] [[project/tests/TESTING#`flexbuffer` (on a field)|`flexbuffer`]]\n    - [ ] [[project/tests/TESTING#`key` (on a field)|key]]\n    - [ ] [[project/tests/TESTING#'native* *'|`native*`]]\n    - [ ] [[project/tests/TESTING#`hash` (on a field)|hash]] ?\n- [ ] Custom Attributes\n    - [ ] ?","x":4100,"y":1840,"width":580,"height":400},
		{"id":"fa975478eba76e83","type":"text","text":"```cpp\n\tenum Type {\n\t\tNIL,\n\n\t\t// atomic types\n\t\tBOOL,\n\t\tINT,\n\t\tFLOAT,\n\t\tSTRING,\n\n\t\t// math types\n\t\tVECTOR2,\n\t\tVECTOR2I,\n\t\tRECT2,\n\t\tRECT2I,\n\t\tVECTOR3,\n\t\tVECTOR3I,\n\t\tTRANSFORM2D,\n\t\tVECTOR4,\n\t\tVECTOR4I,\n\t\tPLANE,\n\t\tQUATERNION,\n\t\tAABB,\n\t\tBASIS,\n\t\tTRANSFORM3D,\n\t\tPROJECTION,\n\n\t\t// misc types\n\t\tCOLOR,\n\t\tSTRING_NAME,\n\t\tNODE_PATH,\n\t\tRID,\n\t\tOBJECT,\n\t\tCALLABLE,\n\t\tSIGNAL,\n\t\tDICTIONARY,\n\t\tARRAY,\n\n\t\t// typed arrays\n\t\tPACKED_BYTE_ARRAY,\n\t\tPACKED_INT32_ARRAY,\n\t\tPACKED_INT64_ARRAY,\n\t\tPACKED_FLOAT32_ARRAY,\n\t\tPACKED_FLOAT64_ARRAY,\n\t\tPACKED_STRING_ARRAY,\n\t\tPACKED_VECTOR2_ARRAY,\n\t\tPACKED_VECTOR3_ARRAY,\n\t\tPACKED_COLOR_ARRAY,\n\t\tPACKED_VECTOR4_ARRAY,\n\n\t\tVARIANT_MAX\n\t};\n```","x":-740,"y":3040,"width":379,"height":1060},
		{"id":"a05206605ed42c31","type":"text","text":"`{gd} var my_dict:Dictionary = {}`","x":-300,"y":3060,"width":580,"height":60},
